M|Appl|When|
M|Appl|tx|1. **Trace the data flow** - Where does bad value originate? Where used?
M|Appl|tx|2. **Map all checkpoints** - List every point data passes through
M|Appl|tx|3. **Add validation at each layer** - Entry, business, environment, debug
M|Appl|tx|4. **tst each layer** - Try to bypass layer 1, verify layer 2 catches it
M|Exam|Bug|Empty `projectDir` caused `git init` in source code
M|Exam|**Da|**
M|Exam|tx|1. tst setup → empty string
M|Exam|tx|2. `Project.cr(name, '')`
M|Exam|tx|3. `WorkspaceManager.createWorkspace('')`
M|Exam|tx|4. `git init` runs in `process.cwd()`
M|Exam|**Fo|**
M|Exam|- La|`Project.cr()` validates not empty/exists/writable
